verse = \lyricmode {
  Let the clash -- ing cym -- bals ring
to the praise of God our King.
With the clan -- ging cym -- bals' noise
come be -- fore him and re -- joice.
Let the breath of all things liv -- ing
praise him with a migh -- ty sound.
Let your voi -- ces shake the ground.
Praise the Lord! Sing hal -- le -- lu -- jah!
}
